## 📋 **Complete API Reference**

### **Core Functions**
```cpp
// Basic dot operations
Dot create_dot(DotType type, Position pos);
Pattern combine_dots(Dot d1, Dot d2, FlowType flow);
Result execute_pattern(Pattern p, Context ctx);

// Community operations
Community join_community(User u, Community c);
Knowledge share_knowledge(User from, User to, Knowledge k);
Resource allocate_resource(Community c, Resource r, User u);

// Cultural operations
Language translate_pattern(Pattern p, Language from, Language to);
Culture adapt_pattern(Pattern p, Culture target);
Wisdom preserve_tradition(Tradition t, Community c);
```

### **Advanced Functions**
```cpp
// Environmental integration
Ecosystem monitor_ecosystem(Location loc);
Climate predict_climate(Pattern historical, Pattern current);
Biodiversity assess_biodiversity(Ecosystem eco);

// Health systems
Health assess_health(User u, HealthMetrics metrics);
Wellness recommend_wellness(Health h, CulturalContext ctx);
Care coordinate_care(User patient, Community caregivers);

// Educational systems
Learning create_curriculum(CulturalContext ctx, AgeGroup group);
Assessment evaluate_progress(User student, Curriculum c);
Mentorship connect_mentor(User student, User mentor);
```

## 🔒 **Security & Ethics Framework**

### **A. Privacy Protection**
